<h1 id="overview_top">Comserv Application Overview</h1>

<p>The Comserv application is a comprehensive multi-tenant web platform designed to serve multiple domains and provide a wide range of functionalities for different user types. At its core, it's a modular system that enables:</p>

<h2>Core Architecture</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Multi-tenant Architecture:</strong> Supports multiple domains and sites through a single codebase</li>
    <li><strong>Domain-specific Customization:</strong> Each domain can have its own:
        <ul>
            <li>Custom styling and branding</li>
            <li>Specific feature sets</li>
            <li>Unique user management</li>
            <li>Independent data storage</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Modular Design:</strong> Features are implemented as independent modules including:
        <ul>
            <li>ENCY (Encyclopedia of Natural Life)</li>
            <li>BMaster (Beekeeping Management)</li>
            <li>CSC (Computer System Consulting)</li>
            <li>Project Management</li>
            <li>User Management</li>
            <li>File Management</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

